title: Cosmos Indian Store
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian grocery shop and fast food. Dal vadas are vegan and gluten free (fried in canola oil), and medu vadas are vegan. Dosas and utthapam are not vegan but can be requested vegan by asking for canola or coconut oil instead. The specialty drinks are not vegan. Relocated from 734 Massachusetts St in 2014.
